    dc:description "FIG. 6. — Ochotona ozansoyi Sen, 2003 from Küçükçekmece West: A, B, P2 sin; C, P4 or M1 sin; D, P4 or M1 dext; E, M2 sin; F, p3 dext; G, mandible dext in lateral view; H, m1, m2 and alveoli of m3 of the same mandible. Cheek teeth in occlusal view. Black areas, enamel; dotted areas, cement infill." ;
